    <description>Hi fellow liars,
I am suggesting the following 3 changes -
1. Inquisitor needs to kill only 2 targets (and can only attack twice),
2. The targets are notified if the inq finds them in investigation
3. If the inq attacks and kills someone who is not an heretic, he losses the remaining attack charges (He can continue his work like a scorned would, convincing others to kill his target).</description>
    
